- De report text selection command (NVDA+shift+upArrow) nu gracefully reports that there is geen selectie in objects which do not support tekstselectie.
- Fixed de issue where pressing de entertoets on certain Miranda-IM knoppen of links was causing NVDA to freeze. (#440)
- De current line of selection is nu properly respected when spelling of copying de current navigator object.
- Worked around een Windows bug which was causing garbage to be spoken after de name of link controls in Windows Explorer en Internet Explorer dialoogvensters. (#451)
- Een probleem opgelost met de report date en time command (NVDA+f12). Previously, date reporting was truncated on sommige systemen. (#471)
- Fixed de issue where het systeem scherm reader flag was soms inappropriately cleared after interacting met secure Windows schermen. This could cause problemen in applicaties which check het scherm reader flag, including Skype, Adobe Reader en Jart. (#462)
- In een Internet Explorer 6 combo box, de active item is nu reported when it is changed. (#342)


